  "system": {
    "description": "<p><strong>Hatred outlives the hateful.</strong></p><p><em>– Brian Tinsman, Rancor flavor text (Magic the Gathering)</em></p><p>Primal warriors that fight with the power of unbridled anger. The legends speak of their kills almost as their own unique deeds, using the barbarian's name as a past-tense verb.</p><h3>Iconic Barbarians</h3><ul><li><strong>Brock Samson</strong>, <em>The Venture Bros</em></li><li><strong>Conan</strong>, <em>Conan the Barbarian series</em></li><li><strong>Guts</strong>, <em>Berserk</em></li><li><strong>Logen Ninefingers</strong>, <em>First Law Trilogy</em></li></ul><h3>Playing Barbarian</h3><p>The barbarian is a medium-high defense bruiser. Stick to an Enemy's face, and hit them very hard.</p><p><strong>Action:</strong> Attack (Melee)<br /><strong>Move:</strong> Frontline<br /><strong>Starting Pack:</strong> Gladiator or Warrior<br /><strong>Key Stat:</strong> Might<br /><strong>Complexity:</strong> ★★☆☆☆</p><h3>Training</h3><p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Melee<br /><strong>Skills:</strong> Brawl and 3 from either Detect, Influence, Leadership, Mysticism, or Survival</p><p></p><h3><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Class Features</span></h3><table class=\"NormalTable\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:9pt\">Level</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:9pt\">Features</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">1st</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Rage, Wrath</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">2nd</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Aggressor</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">3rd</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Perk</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">4th</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Fearmonger</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">5th</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Perk</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">6th</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Mindless Rancor</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">7th</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Perk</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">8th</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Bloodthirsty</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">9th</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Perk</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"67\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">10th</span></p></td><td style=\"border-left-style:none;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:none\" data-colwidth=\"115\"><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Rip and Tear</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /></p>",
