        "name": "Rage",
        "description": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">While Berserk and wearing Light Armor or no Armor, you reduce damage you take by 1 per damage die, and your attack damage dice are one size larger and can explode.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Further, you can go Berserk after you take damage or as part of making an attack. You remain Berserk this way for 1 minute, unless you end it (no Action) or go Unconscious.</span></p>",
